Package: ghfs
Version: 0.0.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: fuse3
Maintainer: Anand Pilania <pilaniaanand@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/anandpilania/ghfs-cross
Description: Mount GitHub repositories as a read-only virtual filesystem
 GHFS mounts your GitHub repositories as a virtual read-only filesystem
 using FUSE. Browse every file across all your repos as local directories
 with no git cloning required.
 .
 Supports authenticated access (private repos) via a personal access token
 and unauthenticated access for public repos.
